{"tid":831722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"防盗裝置一問","createTime":"2018-09-22T07:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T14:38:18.000Z","uid":149631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0da74f16316ce60d7fa16d18e079ea9b5059d13a","tid":831722,"uid":149631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:58:10.000Z","msg":"近排行街有時經過人地鋪路門口嘅防盗就會響，入去定係走都會響，但又唔係次次都響。不論我帶咩袋出街，個袋入面剩係得鎖鑰、銀包、電話都會有機會響。<br />\n<br />\n雖然啲店員唔會叫我比袋佢check，不過自己都會覺得尷尬。諗返起好似係我換左個銀包之後開始發生，銀包係前排Kate減價經外國網站買返嚟。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知點解會響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/155728_83953886912ae9bf25e5010d192b489b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F155728_83953886912ae9bf25e5010d192b489b.png&h=5e66f021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n附上銀包圖一張。"},{"pid":"42273e3cee6363c3f024ce5f5d4c121a75960f1f","tid":831722,"uid":149631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed32727888013538791e4548bf92b6c7c53ce989","tid":831722,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce3c9e90c11fdd9dee53d2d51bef54e312b09209","tid":831722,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T08:28:09.000Z","msg":"睇下銀包d暗格位，可能有條香口膠型bar code條"},{"pid":"5e995236baee399abbfee20fd31682f0a4e8bf2e","tid":831722,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"可能防盗磁未消"}]}